    "original": "Equal parts terrifying and annoying, the uncanny marksmanship of upper caste goblins has long been thought unobtainable by ordinary, self-respecting humans. With this wondrous potion, however, the discerning warrior can harness some of that latent skill for himself at minor cosmetic cost!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"Equal parts terrifying and annoying, the uncanny marksmanship of upper caste goblins has long been thought unobtainable by ordinary, self-respecting humans. With this wondrous potion, however, the discerning warrior can harness some of that latent skill for himself at minor cosmetic cost!\""
